short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Integration powered by InBound Call Support

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: InBound Call Support integration providing database driven screen pops.  The InBound Call Support app integrates with back-office applications using APIs (Salesforce.com, Zendesk, etc.) By leveraging APIs the InBound Call Support extension will search any internal database and present findings in a new window.  The InBound Call Support app also recognizes any phone number presented in Google Chrome and transforms it into a clickable link for seamless click to dial.
